                  "Celene-hunter's small-fang tastes only air! Adjust!",
                  "Shadow-path reveals new approach! Try different angle!",
                  "Prey-luck only! Next strike will find flesh-home!",
                  "Enstad-trained needs better timing! Watch prey-rhythm!",
